,"uid":279695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"集中5大訴求<br />\n1.撤回逃犯條例，永不重提<br />\n2.撤銷612暴動定性<br />\n3.撤銷示威者控罪並承諾永不追究<br />\n4.全面實行雙普選<br />\n5.成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任(包括警黑勾結元朗恐襲)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W55KbMK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW55KbMK.png&h=8768b2be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1d4cb1217cc380f1e7abd9defada68b05f02bed","tid":1357320,"uid":10180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:51:40.000Z","msg":"喂連登仔唔撚係咁廢呀嘛"},{"pid":"c2cffd7842e670f7d5470333c172d878f01a56b8","tid":1357320,"uid":10180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"一個何君堯浪費咗大家成個月心血？"},{"pid":"919b16006060a67b1d295a28a76feadba6195212","tid":1357320,"uid":78250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"推 721 上環post"},{"pid":"2d3fa0830075c42d2cff2efaebe25f616125d092","tid":1357320,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:54:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2ff665e61be41dd468b6b71816cbf6f73921ea5","tid":1357320,"uid":10180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"3654eaa7761fe9d02dc4df9d31298d0952973222","tid":1357320,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9cfa7a8ba6aa899b6b1926a0334a0104e91f130","tid":1357320,"uid":283662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"727a4c727dadf075ef72c0b6710b4130ea4a02da","tid":1357320,"uid":265046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b23e9794cbd9593e6434e5c9359e7b25d43cc","tid":1357320,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中聯辦亂港</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721西環正式宣言 上環36槍 槍槍打頭 </span></span><br />\n和平示威者被警方惡意攻擊 連開36槍 槍槍打頭 <br />\n更於橋上向下向頭部發射 和平示威者身受重傷 <br />\n警方更用強光阻礙記者拍攝現場情況 <br />\n<br />\n警察之權力已凌駕市民生命財產之上 <br />\n港府警方上至 高官 局長 下至 政府公務員 低級警員 <br />\n協助 中共中聯辦 於 612 - 721 期間 <br />\n不斷以非法及不人道之暴力行為 <br />\n意圖消滅所有持反對聲音的平民 <br />\n卻不作反對 <br />\n反之竟合作出賣港人前途 打壓無辜示威者<br />\n<br />\n【文宣包】<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1356661/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1356661/page/1</a><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">港府已被廢 香港前途未卜</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中共下令香港警察與黑社會合作合法亂港殺人</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人生命安全被中國共產黨及<br />\n香港政府視為政治籌碼<br />\n利用恐怖勢力傷害所有平民<br />\n </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">---------------------------------------</span></span><br />\n中國及港政府所有不人道之行動 <br />\n已令香港不再安全 <br />\n並再難以保持經濟地位及自由民主法治社會<br />\n所有香港人都需參與社會運動 <br />\n保護自己的生命安全 人權自由 民主法治 經濟地位<br />\n以上等等被政府損害的權利<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n---------------------------------------</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4. 全面實行雙普選<br />\n5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲</span></span>"}]}